    <rigor-hint>FULL</rigor-hint>
    <rigor-reason>The integration moment between the Code Page host, the auth bootstrap, the URL parameters, and the shared-lib wrapper — touches the canonical surface the entire R3 project is delivering. Code-review + adr-check verify NFR-02 (no @spaarke/auth import in shared lib reachable from this surface) and ADR-028 binding.</rigor-reason>
    <parallel-group>none</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>false</parallel-safe>
    <parallel-reason>Depends on three predecessors (023, 031, 032) and is the integration point; cannot parallelize with any Wave 2 task</parallel-reason>
