  <notes>
    If Wave 1's `<SendEmailPage />` wrapper API diverges from the FR-04 shape (e.g., named differently, props differ), prefer adapting THIS task's prop mapping to match the wrapper — do NOT modify the wrapper from a Code Page task. Wave 1 owns the wrapper; raise a coordination flag if the prop shape isn't usable.

    The `Xrm` global is available when the Code Page is hosted inside Dataverse — guard usage with `typeof Xrm !== 'undefined'` for local dev safety.

    Empirical finding (CLAUDE.md): DocumentRelationshipViewer is the canonical exemplar — keep this App.tsx structure analogous so future maintainers see the parallel.
  </notes>

